16
00:00:55.620 --> 00:00:58.220
Some of us… don’t even put a whole lot
of thought to it.

17
00:00:58.220 --> 00:00:59.820
We literally do just know.

18
00:00:59.820 --> 00:01:04.590
Like for me, I had a crush on Billy the blue
power ranger when I was 4 and that was that.

19
00:01:04.590 --> 00:01:09.820
For others, it can take a little bit more…
