00:26:36.250 --> 00:26:40.570
This is still the age when kids think kissing
is gross and they’re already being judged

447
00:26:40.570 --> 00:26:42.380
by a purity squad.

448
00:26:42.380 --> 00:26:45.780
Consider how that internalizes this sexual
shame.

449
00:26:45.780 --> 00:26:51.149
Not even out of the gate and there’s a deep-seeded
hang up around sex because puritin America

450
00:26:51.149 --> 00:26:53.580
has passed on it’s fear of sex.

451
00:26:53.580 --> 00:26:58.769
Now… consider this same child but in a home
where their parents do not know they are gay.

452
00:26:58.769 --> 00:27:03.020
And where that element of self would not be
welcome among their family or community.

453
00:27:03.020 --> 00:27:07.269
And then consider if this child is trans instead
— one of the most vulnerable groups of the

454
00:27:07.269 --> 00:27:08.269
queer community.

455
00:27:08.269 --> 00:27:12.880
And all the while, media constantly berates
the public — saying these are things not

456
00:27:12.880 --> 00:27:15.340
suitable to be portrayed to all audiences.

457
00:27:15.340 --> 00:27:20.230
To this child, the messaging that they’re
receiving through media signals is that there’s

458
00:27:20.230 --> 00:27:22.809
something inherently wrong with them, who
they are.

459
00:27:22.809 --> 00:27:26.970
Queer children aren’t so inherently different
that they don’t deserve to be able to see

460
00:27:26.970 --> 00:27:32.279
themselves without having to write a thesis
paper on why Rya is a lesbian.

461
00:27:32.279 --> 00:27:38.340
Nobody’s asking for any explicit acts of
sexuality to be in a film directed at children.

462
00:27:38.340 --> 00:27:43.110
And contrary to popular belief, boys don’t
need to ‘kiss’ or go any further than

463
00:27:43.110 --> 00:27:46.820
that in order for it to be an adequate display
of identity.

464
00:27:46.820 --> 00:27:50.730
Because there is more to homosexuality than
sex.

465
00:27:50.730 --> 00:27:56.549
And if you, a straight person or even a gay
person cannot tell the difference, please

466
00:27:56.549 --> 00:27:59.460
begin making steps to change your thinking.

467
00:27:59.460 --> 00:28:04.629
Every year, the demographic of ‘LGBTQ Youth’
increases.

468
00:28:04.629 --> 00:28:08.659
Every year, the number of adults who identify
as bi-or-pansexual increases.

469
00:28:08.659 --> 00:28:13.700
This isn’t an issue that’s going to go
away and soon there will be an even greater

470
00:28:13.700 --> 00:28:19.769
demand to see these people as human beings
with different social perspectives, rather

471
00:28:19.769 --> 00:28:22.379
than sexual deviants.

472
00:28:22.379 --> 00:28:23.379
And Disney?

473
00:28:23.379 --> 00:28:27.880
They’ve gone out of their way to establish
themselves as the largest producer not only

474
00:28:27.880 --> 00:28:32.899
of children's’ media — but maybe even
just media in general.

475
00:28:32.899 --> 00:28:37.190
Disney has more cultural sway over global
media than any other single institution on

476
00:28:37.190 --> 00:28:42.230
the planet – especially given how ubiquitous
their formative material is.

477
00:28:42.230 --> 00:28:45.460
Disney has a hand in shaping the coming culture
of the world.

478
00:28:45.460 --> 00:28:51.020
I’d say they have a pretty big obligation
to fight back against the repressive purity

479
00:28:51.020 --> 00:28:56.039
values that are still internalizing shame
in children.

480
00:28:56.039 --> 00:29:01.210
Against the illogical puritan fear fear of
sex and it's even more illogical connection

481
00:29:01.210 --> 00:29:02.539
to gay people.

482
00:29:02.539 --> 00:29:08.650
So their active silence of the it’s-okay-to-be-gay
topic is beginning to echo louder than if

483
00:29:08.650 --> 00:29:12.379
they just came out condemning non-straight,
non-cis identities.

484
00:29:12.379 --> 00:29:16.900
It’s like they think they’re being sneaky,
but they’re not.

485
00:29:16.900 --> 00:29:19.990
Even younger people are beginning to pick
up on it.

486
00:29:19.990 --> 00:29:25.360
If we want the next generation of lesbians,
gays, bis, and trans people to grow up feeling

487
00:29:25.360 --> 00:29:31.460
normal, we need to stop putting conditions
and age restrictions on their very identities.

488
00:29:31.460 --> 00:29:36.960
And it starts with us — the audiences — deciding
that we’re not going to tolerate this clear

489
00:29:36.960 --> 00:29:41.490
cultural division between straight and everything
else.

490
00:29:41.490 --> 00:29:48.679
This isn’t a phase, it’s not a condition,
it’s not a choice, and it’s not a development.

491
00:29:48.679 --> 00:29:57.360
We’re never going to be able to be who we
are, if everyone else expects us to be what

492
00:29:57.360 --> 00:30:35.940
they’re afraid of.